Radial¶

In [28]:
X11 = Distribution.radial_binary(pts=300,
               mean=[0, 0],
               st=1,
               ed=2, seed=20)
X22 = Distribution.radial_binary(pts=300,
               mean=[0, 0],
               st=4,
               ed=5, seed=20)

Y11 = np.ones(X11.shape[0])
Y22 = np.zeros(X11.shape[0])

X5 = np.vstack((X11, X22))
y5 = np.hstack((Y11, Y22))
